<item>
            <title>[LU-6421] Failed to set max_pages_per_rpc permanently</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6421</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1. get value of max_pages_per_rpc &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl get_param osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc&lt;br/&gt;
osc.server-OST0000-osc-ffff8800901b9800.max_pages_per_rpc=256&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;2. set it permanently with the value 1024&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl set_param -P osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc=1024&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl get_param osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc&lt;br/&gt;
osc.server-OST0000-osc-ffff8800901b9800.max_pages_per_rpc=1024&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;3. remount OSTs and lustre client&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4. get the value of max_pages_per_rpc again&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl get_param osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc&lt;br/&gt;
osc.server-OST0000-osc-ffff88062e2a2800.max_pages_per_rpc=256&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The value not changed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
